title: This Month's GTA+ Benefits
headline: This Month's GTA+ Benefits
subtitle: GTA+
content:
In addition to the recurring monthly GTA$500,000 deposited directly into your Maze Bank account, GTA+ Members who've signed up for this month (May 29 - June 16) will also receive:

— The Fathom FR36 (Coupe)
— 50% off Executive Office Properties
— 3X Rewards on VIP Work and Challenges
— 40% off Special Vehicles
— The Strapz Patterned Sweatshirt and Jeans
— And more

Membership automatically renews monthly, cancel anytime. Visit rsg.ms/gtaplus for more info.
